</p><p>
The Legend legacy left a near mortally wounded <a href="groups.cfm?mode=detail&org=razor1911">Razor</a> and practically killed <a href="groups.cfm?mode=detail&org=trsi">TRSI</a> on the PC.
This left Razor with no love lost for Legend.
So it wasn't too supprising when at near years end after The Butcher was busted.
That the remaining people at Legend would team up with Razor's main rival, <a href="groups.cfm?mode=detail&org=ptg">Pentagram</a>.
The two would join and then emerge as a new super-group known as <a href="groups.cfm?mode=detail&org=gns">Genesis</a>!
